{"word":"παρεκτός","slug":"παρεκτός","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b><el>παρεϰτός</el></b> [<el><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:παρά\">παρά</a>, <a class=\"S\" href=\"S:ἐκτός\">ἐκτός</a></el>] a function word expressing an exclusionary aspect<b><p class=\"pp3\"/>—<pp>a.</pp></b> as <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ adv.\">adv.</a> <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ funct.\">funct.</a> as <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ adj.\">adj.</a> <b>other</b> <el>χωρὶς τῶν <a class=\"S\" href=\"S:παρεκτός\">παρεκτός</a></el> (= <el>χ. τῶν γινομένων π</el>.) not including the other stuff <b><a href='B:540 11:28'>2 Cor 11:28</a>.<p class=\"pp3\"/>—<pp>b.</pp></b> as <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ prep.\">prep.</a> <b>excluding, except for <a href='B:470 5:32'>Mt 5:32</a>; <a href='B:470 19:9'>19:9</a> <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ v.l.\">v.l.</a>; <a href='B:510 26:29'>Ac 26:29</a>.</b> <center id=\"nav_bottom\"> <a id=\"left_arrow\" href=\"S:παρεκλήθην\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> <a id=\"bottom_home\" href=\"S:#1.Table of Contents\">&emsp;&emsp;</a> <a id=\"right_arrow\" href=\"S:παρέλαβον\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> </center> "}]}